data.description: Welcome Home! This spacious 3 Bedroom home features an updated kitchen with granite countertops, a large island, tons of cabinets including a large pantry, and lots of natural light. Pictures don't do it justice, the kitchen needs to be seen. Step into your cozy family room containing a gas fireplace for easy comfort on cold winter days. All of the bedrooms, including the master, have beautiful hardwood floors. The dining room, living room and stairways have been freshly painted. The fully fenced in back yard boasts a concrete patio and a large shed, perfect for a Man Cave or a She-Shed. Tall bushes line the entire back yard allowing you to entertain guests in private. When the fun in the backyard becomes too much, retire to the home theatre in the basement including a Bose 5.1 surround sound system with Onkyo receiver and a 1080P projector with a framed 10' theater screen. Lots of storage space: easy to access crawlspace, extra space in the 2 car attached garage and the shed in the back yard. Newer appliances in the kitchen. Equipped with home security system. Home warranty offered by seller. Truly a MUST SEE! Seller has an assumable FHA loan at 4.875%.
